long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Channel the unstoppable power of Super Saiyan Goku every time you open a new tab! This Chrome extension transforms your browsing experience with electrifying live wallpapers of Goku in his iconic Super Saiyan form, straight from the legendary Dragon Ball series.

Features:
🎨 High-quality live wallpapers of Super Saiyan Goku, capturing his intense energy.
🌐 Customizable search bar that works with your favorite search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display for an enhanced browsing experience.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for seamless navigation.
Feel the energy of Dragon Ball and let Goku’s legendary transformation inspire you throughout the day. Perfect for fans who want a dynamic and visually stunning new tab experience.
